    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let’s Get Larry a Haircut</strong> is a <strong>2D block-pushing puzzle game</strong> in which you must navigate and manipulate objects in a maze collecting enough tokens to unlock the hairdressing place, then push Larry in there. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With block-pushing and sokoban style gameplay inspired by games like Repton, Boulder Dash and the like, Larry is a relaxing game about not getting crushed or blowing up the wrong things. Also, don’t telefrag Larry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/extras/ecb3c6945cf1aedae6997852e9c644db.poster.avif?t=1741719342\" width=480 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/extras/ecb3c6945cf1aedae6997852e9c644db.webm?t=1741719342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334830/extras/ecb3c6945cf1aedae6997852e9c644db.mp4?t=1741719342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pros:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catchy music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has Bees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You control a sort of 2D cow face</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are time and fewest steps challenges if you like that sort of thing</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cons:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You control a sort of 2D cow face</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not a very realistic depiction of getting haircuts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In fact there's no actual hairdressing action whatsoever</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
